        "template--18850231484751__f5332588-ee9e-4cb8-b588-7497ef23f2f0-16824067253affbd63-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As an email marketer, you'll report directly to the CRM & MA Manager at Loop. Besides the colleagues of your own team, you'll work together closely with other <strong>A-players<\/strong> from the<strong> Customer, Brand, and E-commerce team<\/strong>. You'll be able to own challenging projects, have the freedom to do it your way, and blow the world away with your mesmerising email campaigns!<\/p>",
