          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<ul><li>With a <strong>can-do attitude<\/strong> and a critical mindset<\/li><li>Being able to <strong>manage projects autonomously<\/strong> and take responsibility<\/li><li>Thinking like <strong>Loop‚Äôs customers,<\/strong> in every step of their journey<\/li><li>Hands-on experience with <strong>Emarsys<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Basic code skills<\/strong>: read and edit html\/CSS, setup tracking, events, etc.<\/li><li><strong>A\/B\/N testing <\/strong>methodology to lift Loop‚Äôs strategy to the next level<\/li><li><strong>KPI analysis<\/strong> and data-driven decision-making<\/li><li>Experience in a <strong>CRM\/CDP<\/strong> environment (ability to work with 1+ MIO database) is required<\/li><li>Experience in a <strong>GDPR<\/strong>-oriented company is preferred<\/li><li>Experience in a globally present <strong>DTC company<\/strong> is a big plus!<\/li><\/ul>",
            "description_padding": 32
